[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11423] added more specific errors for missing values in records
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11289] allowed spreading arguments to commands
nibon7 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11422] fixed a panic when 
``http_client``
 fails
, and improved redirection: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11421] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11384] 2
