[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11416] simplified the feature gates for 
``stor``
 commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11415] made polars deps optional for 
``cargo test --all``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11414] limited direct construction of 
``Record``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11409] added a check for clean repo after tests
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11407] fixed sandboxing of redirection tests
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11406] bumped the reedline development version
