[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11428] fixed a bug with "bytes remove --end" .
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11424] removed the unnecessary 
``replace_in_variable``
lavafroth implemented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11403] fix: prevent greedy matching of directory names
cyradotpink 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11329] allowed 
``http``
 commands' automatic redirect-following to be disabled
